metadata.name: Hiroshige x Kiki
metadata.description:
Hiroshige x Kiki
Artwork by Mannay (2022)

————————————————————

This illustration is inspired by an Utagawa Hiroshige ukiyo-e from 1841 as well as Kiki from Kiki's Delivery Service, the 1989  animated film written and directed by Hayao Miyazaki.

Digitized using Photoshop. 

————————————————————

Artwork size: 3500 × 2303px
